original: This Currency was used in Chernarus before the Disease. It is now only used for trading.
english: This Currency was used in Chernarus before the Disease. It is now only used for trading.
czech: Tahle měna byla používána v Černarusi před nákazou. Nyní se používá pouze pro obchodování.
german: Diese Währung wurde in Chernarus vor dem Ausbruch genutzt. Sie wird nun lediglich für den Handel benutzt.
russian: Эта валюта использовалась в Черноруссии до апокалипсиса. И по сей день не потеряла своей ценности.
polish: Waluta która była używana w Chernarus przed wirusem. Teraz używana tylko do handlowania.
hungarian: This Currency was used in Chernarus before the Disease. It is now only used for trading.
italian: This Currency was used in Chernarus before the Disease. It is now only used for trading.
spanish: Esta moneda se usó en Chernarus antes de la enfermedad. Ahora solo se utiliza para el comercio.
french: Cette monnaie était utilisée à Chernarus avant la maladie. Elle est maintenant utilisée pour l'achat et la vente d'objets.
chinese: This Currency was used in Chernarus before the Disease. It is now only used for trading.
japanese: This Currency was used in Chernarus before the Disease. It is now only used for trading.
portuguese: Este dinheiro era usado em Chernarus antes da pandemia. Agora é usado apenas para negociações.
chinesesimp: This Currency was used in Chernarus before the Disease. It is now only used for trading.
